10. Create 2D list to DataFrame
lists = [[1, 'aaa', 22], [2, 'bbb', 25], [3, 'ccc', 24]]

lists = [[1, 'aaa', 22], [2, 'bbb', 25], [3, 'ccc', 24]]
import pandas as pd
import numpy as np
lists = [[1, 'aaa', 22], [2, 'bbb', 25], [3, 'ccc', 24]]
arr= np.array( lists)
df=pd.DataFrame(arr)
print(df)
(ou)   0    1   2
0  1  aaa  22
1  2  bbb  25
2  3  ccc  24
